> ## River Sprite
>*Small elemental, neutral*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 10
> - **Hit Points** 20(4d6+6)
> - **Speed** 30ft., swim 60ft.
>___
>|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
>|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
>|8 (-1)|12 (+1)|12 (+1)|9 (-1)|12 (+1)|9 (-1)|
>___
> - **Damage Immunities** Fire, Poison
> - **Damage Resistance** Acid
> - **Condition Immunities** Poisoned
> - **Senses** passive Perception 10
> - **Languages** Aquan
> - **Challenge** 1/2 (100 XP)
> ___
> ***Water Form. *** While in water, this creature counts as invisible
> ### Actions
> ***Slam.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. *Hit:* 5 (2d4) bludgeoning damage
>
> ***Jet Stream Recharge(3).***  The River Sprite violently launches a 15-ft cone of water from itself.  Creatures in this area must succeed on a DC 10 Dexterity saving throw, or take 7 (2d4+2) bludgeoning damage and be knocked prone.
___
> ## Wind Sprite
>*Small elemental, neutral*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 13
> - **Hit Points** 17(5d6)
> - **Speed** 30ft., fly 60ft.
>___
>|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
>|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
>|6 (-2)|14 (+2)|9 (-1)|9 (-1)|14 (+2)|9 (-1)|
>___
> - **Damage Immunities** Poison
> - **Damage Resistance** Bludgeoning, Piercing, and Slashing From Nonmagical Weapons
> - **Condition Immunities** Poisoned
> - **Senses** passive Perception 10
> - **Languages** Auran
> - **Challenge** 1/2 (100 XP)
> ___
> ### Actions
> ***Slam.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. *Hit:* 3 (1d6) slashing damage
>
> ***Whirlwind Recharge(3).***  The Wind Sprite violently launches slashing air from itself in a 5-foot radius.  Creatures in this area must succeed on a DC 12 Dexterity saving throw, or take 7 (2d4+2) slashing damage and is knocked 10 feet away from the Wind Sprite.

