> ## Lightning Sprite
>*Small elemental, neutral*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 15
> - **Hit Points** 13(2d8 + 4)
> - **Speed** 45ft., fly 90ft.
>___
>|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
>|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
>|6 (-2)|16 (+3)|10 (+0)|9 (-1)|12 (+1)|9 (-1)|
>___
> - **Damage Immunities** Poison, Lightning, Thunder
> - **Condition Immunities** Poisoned
> - **Senses** passive Perception 10
> - **Languages** Auran
> - **Challenge** 1/2 (100 XP)
> ___
> ***Death Burst.***  When the Lightning Sprite dies it explodes ina shower of sparks.  Each creature within 5 feet of the Lightning Sprite must succeed on a DC 13 Dexterity saving throw or take 4 (1d8) lightning damage.
> ### Actions
> ***Multiattack***  The Lightning Sprite makes two claw attacks
> ***Claw.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. *Hit:* 3 (1d4+1) slashing damage
>
> ***Static Strike Recharge(2).***  The Lightning Sprite's claws arc with a deadly charge.  Its next melee attack does an additional 1d8 damage and has advanatage against foes in metal armor.

