> ## Giant Mosquito
>*Medium beast, unaligned*
> ___
> - **Armor Class** 13
> - **Hit Points** 13 (3d8)
> - **Speed** 10 ft., fly 50 ft., swim 50 ft.
>___
>|STR|DEX|CON|INT|WIS|CHA|
>|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|:---:|
>|10 (+0)|14 (+2)|10 (+0)|1 (-5)|10 (+0)|3 (-4)|
>___
> - **Senses** passive Perception 19
> - **Challenge** 1/2 (100 XP)
> ___
> ### Actions
> ***Drain Blood.*** *Melee Weapon Attack:* +4 to hit, reach 5ft., one target. *Hit:* 5 (1d6 + 2).  The target must succeed on a DC 13 Strength saving throw or take 9 (2d8) poison damage and becomes grappled.  Half of the poison damage dealt in this way is returned to the Giant Mosquito as temporary hit points.

